WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.740 --> 00:00:03.940
Huo Jiuling, you deliberately leaked this information to me,

2
00:00:03.940 --> 00:00:05.660
allowing my pursuers to arrest him,

3
00:00:05.880 --> 00:00:06.860
and you even offered land

4
00:00:07.140 --> 00:00:09.160
worth ten billion, to

5
00:00:09.540 --> 00:00:11.040
have me play along.

6
00:00:11.520 --> 00:00:12.440
From my investigation,

7
00:00:12.860 --> 00:00:16.140
this girl is this man's girlfriend.

8
00:00:17.920 --> 00:00:19.320
I'm furious!

9
00:00:19.600 --> 00:00:20.340
No way?

10
00:00:20.360 --> 00:00:21.020
Huo Jiuling,

11
00:00:21.400 --> 00:00:22.800
you made me participate in this charade,

12
00:00:23.080 --> 00:00:24.300
all for this woman?

13
00:00:24.760 --> 00:00:26.840
You played along; that land is yours.

14
00:00:27.660 --> 00:00:28.760
Don't worry about anything else.

15
00:00:28.760 --> 00:00:31.620
Tomorrow, I'll have my lawyer transfer the deed to you discreetly.

16
00:00:31.860 --> 00:00:33.540
However,

17
00:00:34.200 --> 00:00:37.540
in addition to your Sicily property, I also want the Milan property.

18
00:00:38.220 --> 00:00:41.340
Consider it compensation for you destroying my camera.

19
00:00:41.880 --> 00:00:44.320
What?  You seem reluctant.

20
00:00:44.800 --> 00:00:47.160
Not giving me the Milan property is also acceptable.

21
00:00:49.260 --> 00:00:52.220
Little girl, there's something I forgot to mention.

22
00:00:52.620 --> 00:00:53.960
I forgot to tell you.

23
00:00:54.860 --> 00:00:55.200
What?

24
00:00:57.380 --> 00:00:59.280
She... is Hong Jiu.

25
00:01:00.800 --> 00:01:01.640
Huo Jiuling,

26
00:01:02.080 --> 00:01:05.460
I'll wait for your contract tomorrow. Take this man away.

27
00:01:08.900 --> 00:01:10.420
Leilei, Leilei, help me!

28
00:01:10.600 --> 00:01:13.840
They stormed the tomb on Zhilingshan and beat me, breaking my ribs.

29
00:01:13.920 --> 00:01:14.960
I'll take you to the hospital.

30
00:01:16.100 --> 00:01:17.360
Huo Jiuling, what are you doing?

31
00:01:17.840 --> 00:01:20.180
Zhilin, when did I say I'd take you to the hospital?

